In standard QFT,  $i\varepsilon$  prescription is valid and vital from both mathematics and physics. It not only cures the divergent problems in mathematics, but also ensures that physically the quantum system can evolve from the non-interacting vacuum state in the infinitely past to the true vacuum state with interaction at present.

